===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|Rin|Rīn|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|Rīnaz|lang=en}}, from {{etyl|cel|en}}. The spelling with ''Rh-'' is because of the influence of Greek {{term|Ῥῆνος|tr=Rhēnos}}.

