* {{IPA|/raɪn/}}
* {{audio|en-us-Rhine.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|aɪn}}

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun|head=the Rhine}}

# A river that flows through Switzerland, Germany, west [[Bavaria]], France, Belgium, and the Netherlands.

